cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CYBER, cs.CL

This paper deals with the evaluation of a recommender system in an Ed-Tech application, which involves user behavior analysis and algorithm comparison. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), followed by Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, since the paper deals with data collection and analysis, Cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) could also be a possible sub-category. Finally, since the recommender system involves natural language processing, Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) could also be a possible sub-category.
